The Breath of Suspension is a collection of science fiction stories by American writer Alexander Jablokov. It was released in 1994 and was the author's first book published by Arkham House . It was published in an edition of 3,496 copies. the stories originally appeared in Isaac Asimov's Science Fiction Magazine.
